Dates and Times:

How do you get the current date and time?
  Time.now

How do you find just the Year? Month? Hour? Second? Weekday?
  Year: Date.today.strftime("%Y") => "2017"
  Month: Date.today.strftime("%B") => "April"
  Weekday: Date.today.strftime("%A") => "Saturday"
  Hour: Time.now.strftime("%H") => "17"
  Hour: Time.now.strftime("%I") => "05"

  Minute: Time.now.strftime("%M")
  Second: Time.now.strftime("%S")
  Time.now.strftime("%p") => gives PM or AM

